WEST FLAGLER AMUSEMENT CO., Inc., Appellant, v. CORAL WAY AMUSEMENT CORPORATION and Dewey Knight, Appellees (two cases). Nos. 6637, 6638. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. March 22, 1933. Leonard Epstein, of Miami, Fla., for appellant. Robert C. Lane and Geo. L. Patterson, both of Miami, Fla., for appellees.

Before BRYAN, FOSTER, and SIBLEY, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment is affirmed.
